Deputy President William Ruto will be the guest of honour at this year's Sanaa Theatre Awards. Awards founder and director George Orido said in a statement, "I was privileged and humbled to meet William Ruto at the Hustler's mansion, where we discussed matters theatre in Kenya." Adding, "He agreed to our request to grace the 6th edition of the event." The event will take place at the Kenyan National Theatre on December 17.